comments: Hood (POR) makes contact with Porzingis' (DAL) body that affects his shot attempt at the basket.
Brunson (DAL) makes contact to Bazemore's (POR) arm that affects his ability to gather the rebound.
McCollum (POR) maintains a legal guarding position on Doncic (DAL) and cleanly deflects the ball away.
Hezonja (POR) briefly grasps Curry (DAL) but the contact does not affect his FOM.
Finney-Smith (DAL) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Hezonja's (POR) path.
Hezonja (POR) makes marginal contact with Doncic (DAL) that does not affect his SQBR.
Doncic (DAL) and Bazemore (POR) make incidental contact with each other during the loose ball.
A 24 second violation was correctly called.
Doncic (DAL) makes marginal contact with Lillard (POR) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Bazemore (POR) and  Porzingis (DAL) engage and disengage during the rebound.

Replay review of the personal foul called on Lillard (POR) for contact with Finney-Smith (DAL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Lillard legally deflected the ball from Finney-Smith during his shot attempt and any body contact by Lillard did not affect the shot attempt.
Brunson (DAL) commits a take foul on Bazemore (POR).
Hezonja (POR) and Doncic (DAL) make incidental foot to foot contact during the rebound.
